::Shadow Wing::

She returned to her bed and layed down.  After the long day, she needed 
sleep.  But after her mistake earlier, she was more wary.  She transformed 
into her owl mode and flew up into the rafters in the ceiling.  She found a 
nise corner to hide in and she slept.

Her instincts would wake her for her night time hunt.
